<br>
--------- Event #1 ---------<br>
When: Approximately May 25.<br>
Where: To be determined<br>
What: Fun and games incuding minstrel roller-coaster rides, contests, prizes, destruction, and mayhem.  Basically a summer picnic with friends, egg salad, and blood!  There will be several emerald prizes: a stack of 35 emerald seals.  Several sapphire prizes: a stack of 35 sapphire seals.  And at least 2 diamond prizes: a stack of 20 DIAMOND seals.  So plan on joining FT, People's Front, Paradox, and Sacred Order for a bunch o' fun!<br>
<br>
Further details will be posted in the near future.  If you have any comments, suggestions, or just want to volunteer to help out send me an email at scottcm@usa.net.<br>
<br>
Special thanks to Ranbas for donating 20 diamond seals!!  Also thanks to Krystl for donating 11 diamond seals and Nerise for donating 4 diamond seals and more than a few sapphire seals.<br>
<br>
--------- Event #2 ---------<br>
When: Tue. &amp; Thu (April 30 &amp; May 2) 8pm CST.<br>
Where: Darkness Falls<br>
What:  In order to give away all those prizes we need to collect some seals.  Emerald and Sapphire seals are needed the most.  I'd rather collect seals in this fashion than ask people to donate from their personal stash.  FEEL FREE TO SCHEDULE YOUR OWN SEAL HUNTS!  Again, we can use the help collecting seals. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   As a benefit we'll have some good company and exp while we collect the seals.  If you collect any seals for Event #1 you can turn them into a guild officer.  Sykosis currently has the stash of seals collected so far (and for a large bribe will discreetly slip a few to you - just don't tell Krystl or Ranbas!).<br>
<br>
--------- Event #3 ---------<br>
When: This weekend (reply to this post and suggest either Sat or Sun and a time that works best for you.  I'll post the official time on Thursday).<br>
Where: Meet at Cotswold then off to where ever we choose.<br>
What:  No goal, no real structure, just a chance to group with guildies/alliance members/friends of the guild and have some fun.  We'll decide as a group what to do.<br>
